Growth mode for HIP-3

To bootstrap novel markets, HIP-3 deployers can activate growth mode to reduce fees by 90%. Growth mode applies on top of other multipliers, such as aligned stablecoin collateral fee benefits and staking discounts.

@tradexyz enabled growth mode today for their perp assets, lowering baseline taker fees to 0.009%.

